Class StudentTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.pdx.cs410J.InvokeMainTestCase
      • edu.pdx.cs410J.whitlock.StudentTest

  • public class StudentTest
extends InvokeMainTestCase
    JUnit tests for the Student class. These tests extend InvokeMainTestCase which allows them to easily invoke the main method of Student. They also make use of the hamcrestmatchers for more readable assertion statements.
